<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM13.1">
<l>kaṇṇa ṉeṉṉuṅ karunteyvam kāṭci paḻakik kiṭappēṉaip</l>
<l>puṇṇiṟ puḷippey tāṟpōlap puṟaniṉ ṟaḻaku pēcātē</l>
<l>peṇṇiṉ varutta maṟiyāta perumā ṉaraiyiṟ pītaka</l>
<l>vaṇṇa vāṭai koṇṭeṉṉai vāṭṭan taṇiya vīcīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Do not stand aside and speak pretty [words]</l>
<l rend="indent">as if pouring tamarind [juice] on a wound</l>
<l>About me who am used to the sight of the black god called Kṛṣṇa!</l>
<l>Take the yellow-hued robes from the waist of the Lord who does not know </l>
<l rend="indent">of a woman’s suffering,</l>
<l>and fan [me with it] so that my distress is soothed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
